SELECT DISTINCT CMDES.IBBUYE AS PROFILACHETEUR, CMDES.IBFACI AS ETABLISSEMENT, CMDES.IBWHLO AS DEPOT, DEPOT.MWWHNM AS LIBDPT, CMDES.IBITNO AS CODEARTICLE, ARTICLE.MMITCL AS GRPRODUIT, ARTICLE.MMITGR AS GRPARTICLE,
ARTICLE.MMITDS AS DESIGNATION, CMDES.IBPUNO AS NUMOA, CMDES.IBORTY AS TYPECMDES, DATEC.IAPUDT AS DATECMDES, CMDES.IBSUNO AS FOURNISSEUR, FOURN.IDSUNM AS NOMFOURNISSEUR, CMDES.IBPUST AS STATUTHAUT, CMDES.IBPUSL AS STATUTBAS,
CMDES.IBORQA AS QUANTITE,CMDES.IBODI1 AS REMISE1, CMDES.IBODI2 AS REMISE2, CMDES.IBODI3 AS REMISE3, CMDES.IBLNAM AS MONTANT
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT IBBUYE, IBFACI, IBWHLO, IBITNO, IBPUNO, IBSUNO, IBPUST, IBPUSL, IBORQA, IBLNAM, IBODI1,IBODI2,IBODI3, IBORTY FROM M3FDBCM1.MPLINE
WHERE IBPUSL!=99 AND IBITNO IN (SELECT MMITNO FROM M3FDBCM1.MITMAS WHERE MMCONO=100 AND MMITTY!='E99' AND MMITCL IN ('91003','93001','93002','93003','93004','93006','93007','94001','95003','95012','93001','95003'))
AND IBPUNO IN (SELECT DISTINCT IAPUNO FROM M3FDBCM1.MPHEAD WHERE IACONO=100 AND IAORTY IN ('E01','E02','OPT') AND (IAPUDT>20181231 AND IAPUDT<20220101))) AS CMDES
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT IAPUNO,IAPUDT, IASUNO FROM M3FDBCM1.MPHEAD WHERE IACONO=100 AND IAORTY IN ('E01','E02','OPT') AND (IAPUDT>20181231 AND IAPUDT<20220101)) AS DATEC ON CMDES.IBPUNO=DATEC.IAPUNO
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT MMITNO, MMITDS, MMITGR, MMITCL FROM M3FDBCM1.MITMAS WHERE MMCONO=100) AS ARTICLE ON CMDES.IBITNO=ARTICLE.MMITNO
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT IDSUNO, IDSUNM FROM M3FDBCM1.CIDMAS WHERE IDSUTY=0 AND IDSTAT=20 AND IDCONO=100) AS FOURN ON CMDES.IBSUNO=FOURN.IDSUNO
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT MWWHLO, MWWHNM FROM M3FDBCM1.MITWHL WHERE MWCONO=100) AS DEPOT ON CMDES.IBWHLO=DEPOT.MWWHLO
ORDER BY IBFACI, IBPUNO,IBITNO
